<item>
            <title>[HIVE-13729] FileSystem$Cache leaks in FileUtils.checkFileAccessWithImpersonation</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/HIVE-13729</link>
                <project id="12310843" key="HIVE">Hive</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Didn&apos;t invoke FileSystem.closeAllForUGI after checkFileAccess. This results leak in FileSystem$Cache and eventually OOM for HS2.&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;Workaround without fix - &lt;br/&gt;
fs.hdfs.impl.disable.cache=true&lt;br/&gt;
fs.file.impl.disable.cache=true&lt;/p&gt;</description>
